              <p>128 Greenpoint Ave, Brooklyn, NY</p>
              <p>
                Breezy Mexican restaurant Oxomoco in Greenpoint keeps its one
                star. Expect beef tartare tostadas, lamb barbacoa tacos, and
                market corn tlayudas.
              </p>
              <a href="/restaurants/61f02b3934da66dd0d690e3f"
                ><button class="btn btn-primary">Visit Oxomoco</button>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <img
