              "
              class="card-img"
              alt="Cote Korean Steakhouse
              "
            />
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="card-title">Cote Korean Steakhouse</h3>
              <p>16 W 22nd St, New York, NY</p>
              <p>
                The Korean steakhouse from owner Simon Kim and chef David Shim
                retains one star. The butcherâ€™s feast, which includes four cuts
